how much can i charge per sq ft to paint the inside of a house do i charge extra for the ceiling you can't base it on the sq footage of the house but have to base it on the sq footage of the walls you are painting like i said in an answer yesterday a sq ft house is not the same as the next sq ft house it depends on the height of the ceilings how many windows and doors you have to paint around whether you are painting crown molding whether there are vaulted ceilings type of paint used repairs to the walls that may be required and if they have to be primed if also varies greatly from one community to another i had a house painted a few years ago for sq ft but if that same house was in the town i live in now it would be twice that Sistine Chapel Architecture of the California missions Bungalow Wilton House Xanadu House Wood carving Molding (decorative) Sento Casting McMansion Wallpaper group Pantheon, Rome Basement Eastern Orthodox Church Paint TARDIS Vault Fan (implement) Stucco Lighting Black Mesa Research Facility Door Blenheim Palace Duomo di Siena Abbey Strap-on dildo Fire fighting Palazzo Vecchio Cathedral of Magdeburg Air-raid shelter Doom engine Wayne Corporation Rathfarnham Indoor soccer Michelangelo Alhambra Prime Minister of the United Kingdom Wolfenstein: Enemy Territory Bratislava Castle First-person shooter Norbert Wiener Insulation Stairway Grace Cossington Smith Shotgun house Items in the Metroid series Lichfield Cathedral Cave painting Electrical wiring Caracas Welding Timber framing Giovanni Battista Cipriani School bus Jumpstart 3rd Grade St Albans Cathedral Sundial De Lorean DMC-12 Domus Aurea Arcade cabinet Luca Signorelli Porsche 993 Japanese tea ceremony Star Wars: Battlefront Diagon Alley Manorialism The Time Machine World Trade Center Carpet Bubble Bobble Volleyball Super Metroid Ca' Rezzonico The Haunted Mansion Cathedral architecture Diamond cut Property tax Rachel Whiteread Serenity (Firefly vessel) Natural Selection (computer game) Saw II B